        "title": "DraftKings rises on Senate's sports events, prediction markets bill",
        "description": "<p>Yahoo Finance Head of News Myles Udland takes a look at some of Monday morning's <a data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/markets/stocks/trending/\">trending tickers</a> and stories.</p>\n<p>US senators have introduced a <a data-i13n=\"cpos:2;pos:1\" href=\"https://www.wsj.com/finance/regulation/lawmakers-to-introduce-bipartisan-bill-banning-sports-bets-on-prediction-markets-17d2e272?gaa_at=eafs&gaa_n=AWEtsqesVUbxw0pqzMDovG0lHxwqH6Cb-pPKat_Nq1EqXoeIPCMXIvDdA_nhhlOZwKc%3D&gaa_ts=69c13ce3&gaa_sig=Jj-xmgpGSqRNbEyPqhZ77y_ttLYwkDVE6Kg0JKnT-dQuwZLmcW_SqcYu3eEbB9kayaLnIrnOW4Da3zV4ZLkjiA%3D%3D\">bipartisan bill</a> to ban sports betting from prediction markets. DraftKings (<a data-i13n=\"cpos:3;pos:1\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/quote/DKNG\">DKNG</a>) stock is moving higher on the news.</p>\n<p>Synopsys (<a data-i13n=\"cpos:4;pos:1\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/quote/SNPS\">SNPS</a>) stock is rising on a <a data-i13n=\"cpos:5;pos:1\" href=\"https://www.wsj.com/business/deals/activist-elliott-builds-big-stake-in-chip-design-software-maker-synopsys-4bf88127\">Wall Street Journal report</a> that Elliott Investment Management has built a multibillion-dollar stake in the company.</p>\n<p>Elon Musk's Tesla (<a data-i13n=\"cpos:6;pos:1\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/quote/TSLA\">TSLA</a>) and SpaceX (<a data-i13n=\"cpos:7;pos:1\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/quote/SPAX.PVT\">SPAX.PVT</a>) are teaming up to build a large chip complex in Texas.</p>",
